1973;;Gawain and the Green Knight;;British;;Stephen Weeks;;Murray Head, Ciaran Madden, Nigel Green;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gawain_and_the_Green_Knight_(1973_film);;The mysterious Green Knight appears before King Arthur's court in the New Year and demands the head of Sir Gawain as the prize in a bizarre game. Given a year's grace, Gawain sets off in search of the Knight for a rematch.